The '''Senate Library''', by the [[Time/Legends|time]] of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] known as the '''Old Senate Library''', was the library of the [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Galactic Senate]]. It was on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. Its records included the services of various [[Senator/Legends|senators]] and their aides. [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] apparently purged it of his own records after coming into power.

